---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Canon EF 300mm f2.8L IS II USM">

    <main class="main">

    <!-- Page Title -->
    <div class="page-title">
      <div class="breadcrumbs">
        <nav aria-label="breadcrumb">
          <ol class="breadcrumb">
            <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="/"><i class="bi bi-house"></i> Home</a></li>
            <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="/portfolio">Portfolio</a></li>
            <li class="breadcrumb-item active current">Canon EF 300mm f2.8L IS II USM</li>
          </ol>
        </nav>
      </div>

      <div class="container section-title pb-0">
        <h2>Canon EF 300mm f2.8L IS II USM</h2>
        <div class="title-shape">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 200 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M 0,10 C 40,0 60,20 100,10 C 140,0 160,20 200,10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div><!-- End Section Title -->
    </div><!-- End Page Title -->

    <!-- Portfolio Details Section -->
    <section id="portfolio-details" class="portfolio-details section">

      <div class="container">

        <div class="row gy-4 g-lg-5">
          <div class="col-lg-6">
            <img src="/assets/img/portfolio/56.webp" class="img-fluid mb-4 rounded-4" alt="" loading="lazy">
            <img src="/assets/img/portfolio/57.webp" class="img-fluid mb-4 rounded-4" alt="" loading="lazy">
            <img src="/assets/img/portfolio/58.webp" class="img-fluid mb-4 rounded-4" alt="" loading="lazy">
            <img src="/assets/img/portfolio/59.webp" class="img-fluid mb-4 rounded-4" alt="" loading="lazy">
            <img src="/assets/img/portfolio/60.webp" class="img-fluid mb-4 rounded-4" alt="" loading="lazy">
          </div>

          <div class="col-lg-6">

            <div class="position-sticky" style="top: 40px">
              <div class="portfolio-description">
                <h2>Overview</h2>
                <p>
                  High-detail CAD model of the Canon EF 300mm f/2.8L IS II USM lens, developed from image references with focus on precision surface modeling and realistic external detailing.
                </p>

                <div class="portfolio-info mt-5">
                  <h2>Specifications</h2>
                  <ul>
                    <li><strong>Model:</strong> Canon EF 300mm f/2.8L IS II USM</li>
                    <li><strong>Source:</strong> Image-based reference modeling</li>
                    <li><strong>Detail Level:</strong> High-fidelity external geometry</li>
                    <li><strong>Assembly:</strong> 10-part component assembly</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>

                <h2>Design Constraints</h2>
                <p>
                  <ul>
                    <li>Reconstruct accurate proportions and geometry from image references</li>
                    <li>Maintain high surface quality across cylindrical and curved features</li>
                    <li>Integrate multiple components without visible discontinuities</li>
                    <li>Ensure realistic mechanical behavior for rotating front section</li>
                  </ul>
                </p>

                <h2>Design Approach</h2>
                <p>
                  The model was developed using reference images to capture the external form and detailed surface features of the lens body.
                  <br><br>
                  Individual components were modeled separately and assembled to form a complete system, with rotational motion applied to the front section to replicate real-world lens behavior.
                </p>

                <h2>Key Features</h2>
                <p>
                  <ul>
                    <li>Highly detailed external surface modeling</li>
                    <li>Multi-part assembly with clean component integration</li>
                    <li>Rotational front section simulating lens adjustment</li>
                    <li>Accurate visual representation of a professional camera lens</li>
                  </ul>
                </p>

                <h2>Outcome</h2>
                <p>
                  Delivered a high-fidelity lens model demonstrating advanced surface modeling, assembly structuring, and controlled motion implementation for realistic visualization.
                </p>

              </div>

              <div class="portfolio-info mt-5">
                <h3>Project information</h3>
                <ul>
                  <li><strong>Category</strong> Independent Project</li>
                  <li><strong>Project date</strong> August, 2024</li>
                  <li><strong>Project URL</strong> <a href="https://grabcad.com/library/canon-ef-300mm-f-2-8l-is-ii-usm-lens-1">https://grabcad.com/library/canon-ef-300mm-f-2-8l-is-ii-usm-lens-1</a></li>
                  <li><strong>Workflow Recording</strong> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CGyYC3JCkLI">YouTube Video</a></li>
                  <li><a href="https://grabcad.com/library/canon-ef-300mm-f-2-8l-is-ii-usm-lens-1" class="btn-visit align-self-start">Download CAD Files</a></li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

    </section><!-- /Portfolio Details Section -->

    </main>

</BaseLayout>